did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle: David J. Skorton Presidential Liaison records, 2006-2014.
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: The collection includes files from David Skorton.

bioghist.head: BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE
bioghist.p: David J. Skorton was inaugurated as president of Cornell University on September 7th, 2006.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Records chronicle meetings between President David Skorton and alumni and friends of the University, foundation representatives and corporate representatives..

descgrp.head: INFORMATION FOR USERS

accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions:
accessrestrict.p: Restricted to permission of office of origin.

prefercite.head: Cite As:
prefercite.p: David J. Skorton Presidential Liaison records, #3-15-3682. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.

descgrp.p: The Cornell University Archives Web Archive has a collection copies of speeches and essays given by President Skorton here: https://wayback.archive-it.org/2566/20140615194654/http:/cornell-classic.univcomm.cornell.edu/president/speeches/#
